  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study to determine the safety and efficacy of Mobic® ampoules in the initiation of treatment
      of painful exacerbations of osteoarthritis, rheumatoid arthritis and other similar painful
      inflammatory conditions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
